labelData.lbl_updateBank_Disclaimer:
You may terminate this instruction at any time by giving written notice to the Bank and to UDC Finance Ltd.
Should you dispute any Direct Debit initiated upon your nominated account within 9 months for the first Direct Debit, then we as the initiator must produce evidence of your Instructions and Confirmation within 10 Business Days. Should we fail to do so, then your bank may reverse the Direct Debit(s).
Should you not be satisfied that the instructions you have given authorize us to Direct Debit your nominated account, your Bank may reverse the Direct Debit(s).
If the disputed transaction is outside of the 9 month period, then the dispute will be resolved without Bank intervention (Unless the transaction is the result of forgery, fraud or error).
A letter of confirmation will be sent to you within the next 5 working days which will include the Terms and Conditions of the Direct Debit Authority.
